             was indicted for <rs id="t17930410-98-off526" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17930410-98-off526" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930410-98-off526" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17930410-98-cd527" type="crimeDate">21st of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930410-98-off526 t17930410-98-cd527"></join>, a bushel and a half of coals, value 1 s. 6 d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               <persName id="t17930410-98-person912">
                  Thomas
                   Lowndes
               <interp inst="t17930410-98-person912" type="surname" value="Lowndes"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930410-98-person912" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17930410-98-person912" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
