                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930410-98-defend911 t17930410-98-punish532"></join>
               Publickly whipped at Bride's Wharf
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. COMMON SERJEANT.</p>
